name: Episode 2/3: Stay Curious
description:
Deep down inside of us, there's a ton of questions that still unanswered. 
What's this. what's that. how it's done. why it's happened, etc. However, that is precisely what makes us living and intelligent human beings. The curiosity make us feel alive. So, we must continue to seek answers to these questions.
Like old wise man said, "Malu bertanya, sesat di jalan".

--------------------
Episode 1/3: Fins The Soul
